%% F04 — Operator Journey: syncing a downstream project
flowchart LR
    START([Operator invokes\ndidio sync-all]) --> LOAD[Load\ntarget-projects.json]
    LOAD --> LOOP{Next project?}

    LOOP -->|yes| GITCHECK{Is git repo?}
    LOOP -->|no more| REPORT([Print\ncompliance report])

    GITCHECK -->|no| ERROR([Log error,\ncontinue to next])
    ERROR --> LOOP

    GITCHECK -->|yes| ROLLBACK[Create git tag\npre-didio-sync]

    ROLLBACK --> AGENTS[Copy missing\n.claude/agents/]
    AGENTS --> CMDS[Copy missing\n.claude/commands/]
    CMDS --> SETTINGS{settings.json\nexists?}

    SETTINGS -->|no| COPYSETTINGS[Copy from\ntemplate]
    SETTINGS -->|yes| MERGESETTINGS[Merge allow\narrays via jq]

    COPYSETTINGS --> ROOTAGENTS
    MERGESETTINGS --> ROOTAGENTS

    ROOTAGENTS[Copy missing\nroot agents/] --> DOCS[Create docs/adr/\nif missing]
    DOCS --> MEMORY{agent-learnings\nhas content?}

    MEMORY -->|placeholder| SKIP_MEM[Leave as-is]
    MEMORY -->|real content| PRESERVE[Preserve,\ndon't overwrite]

    SKIP_MEM --> GITIGNORE
    PRESERVE --> GITIGNORE

    GITIGNORE[Append .gitignore\nentries if missing] --> CLAUDEMD[Section-sync\nCLAUDE.md]
    CLAUDEMD --> SUMMARY[Print per-project\nsummary]
    SUMMARY --> LOOP
